text: Jürgen Klinge (born 27 June 1940) is a German wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman 97 kg at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1940 births Category:Living people Category:German male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of East Germany Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Leipzig
